# Coulsy Joinery — Netlify redirects
#
# Legacy .html variants (from older build config) are consolidated onto
# their clean-URL equivalents to fix duplicate-indexing in Google.
# Only URLs Google has actually indexed are listed; anything else that
# 404s is fine. Netlify's splat wildcard doesn't suffix-match /*.html,
# so these are enumerated explicitly.

/about.html                      /about                      301!
/contact.html                    /contact                    301!
/joinery-services.html           /joinery-services           301!
/about/compliance.html           /about/compliance           301!
/about/qualifications.html       /about/qualifications       301!
/about/sustainability.html       /about/sustainability       301!
/web-development.html            /                           301!
